# Frontend rules

- React 19 + Next 15 App Router. `"use client"` only when needed.
- One section component per file in `src/components/`.
- **Tailwind semantic tokens only** — `text-ink/fg/soft/muted/faint`,
  `bg-overlay/<a>`, `border-overlay/<a>`, `bg-bg-deep/panel`,
  `brand-blue/purple/cyan/emerald/pink`. No literal `white`/`zinc`.
- Reuse `SectionHeading`, `glass`/`glass-light`, accent-glow blur.
- Framer Motion: entrance via `initial` + `whileInView` (`viewport={{ once:
  true, margin: "-70px" }}`), staggered `delay`.
- Responsive first (mobile → `md:`/`lg:`). No horizontal overflow.
- Inline `style` only for dynamic values (e.g. brand color).
- Content comes from `docs/` — keep the matching doc in sync.
- Add/extend a Vitest test for new logic.
